org.hibernate.sql.ast.tree.spi.from

Class TableSpace

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hibernate.sql.ast.tree.spi.from.TableSpace
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SqlAstNode

    public class TableSpace
extends Object
implements SqlAstNode
    Represents a groups of joined tables. Roughly equivalent to what ANSI SQL calls a <table reference>.

    We further group the individual TableSpecification references into groups to be able to more easily refer to all the tables from a single entity/collection persister as a single group.
